org.apache.chemistry.opencmis.client.api

Interface FileableCmisObject

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CmisObject, CmisObjectProperties, ObjectId
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Document, Folder, Item, Policy

    public interface FileableCmisObject
extends CmisObject
    Fileable CMIS object. A fileable object is an object that can reside in a folder.
